data.name: API Hosting
data.description: APIs provided by the Light Framework, Light CMS and Light Commerce.
data.content: APIs out of the box without customization and this is the easiest way to bring up a site of your own that has all common functionalities along with content management and e-commence. All you need to do is to find a host for your static site and even github.com should work.

data.name: Site Hosting
data.description: Host your entire site including APIs and static contents. Price is on monthly subscription basis.
data.content:
Standard package contains the following:
1. All the standard APIs provided by the Framework, Content Management and E-Commerce.
2. Static Site Template with ability to customize. 

Customized package contains the following:
1. Everything Standard package offers
2. Customized APIs
